txt.en: Even with her newly gained powers bestowed by the Pale Herald, Bratha Tasakh fell to your hand. It seems the Ungoledain may now be utterly extinct.
Bratha Tasakh, chieftain of the Ungoledain, is unwaveringly loyal to Shelob, and guards the way deeper into the Remmorchant.
